criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Diagnosis of CF clinically and by sweat test and/ or genetic testing and/ or nasal
             potential difference

          2. Treatment with one or more chronic medications or regimes;

          3. Willingness by patient or parent to sign consent form;

          4. Parents capable of complying with the program requirements including completing
             self-report questionnaires pre and post intervention completion.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Having significant developmental delay or a mental health diagnosis of psychosis;

          2. Transplant patients;

          3. Participation in other interventional studies within 2 weeks of recruitment or during
             the study period -
